========================================================================
                          PROCESS FLOW LOGIC
                     Floral E-Commerce Website - Florish
========================================================================

------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. USER LOGIN PROCESS FLOW LOGIC
------------------------------------------------------------------------
[Start]
   |
   v
[Input: Email & Password]
   |
   v
[Query: Find user document by email in MongoDB]
   |
   +---> (Found?) --- No ---> [Return: Error 401 Unauthorized]
   |
   +--- Yes ---> [Compare password Bcrypt hashes matchPassword()]
                    |
                    +---> (Match?) --- No ---> [Return: Error 401 Unauthorized]
                    |
                    +--- Yes ---> [Generate Session JWT token]
                                     |
                                     v
                                  [Return: HTTP 200 OK + User Specs + JWT]
                                     |
                                     v
                                  [End]

------------------------------------------------------------------------
2. SECURE CHECKOUT SUBMIT PROCESS FLOW LOGIC
------------------------------------------------------------------------
[Start]
   |
   v
[Inbound JWT Protection check authMiddleware]
   |
   +---> (Session token Valid?) --- No ---> [Return: Error 401 Unauthorized]
   |
   +--- Yes ---> [Read Cart items subdocuments list from database / req]
                    |
                    +---> (Cart empty?) --- Yes ---> [Return: Error 400 Bad Request]
                    |
                    +--- No ---> [Create Order document details in MongoDB]
                                    |
                                    v
                                 [Decrement Stock quantity in Products DB]
                                    |
                                    v
                                 [Clear Shopping Cart items collection]
                                    |
                                    v
                                 [Return: HTTP 201 Created + Invoice Specs]
                                    |
                                    v
                                 [End]
